[00:00] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Hi everyone. We\'re excited to introduce the new 3D shape effect in HANA, [music] letting you design with 3D and 2D at the same time on the same canvas and all in real time. Everything works together seamlessly, [music] making 3D creation just as fast and'

[00:12] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'intuitive as working with 2D shapes. To get started, go to Hana File, select any shape on the canvas, then head to the inspector panel on the right [music] and find the effects section. Click the'

[00:24] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'plus icon. Add an effect and choose 3D shape. The effect appears in your effects list where you can enable or disable it. Once applied, you\'ll see a range of'

[00:38] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'adjustable properties, including geometry, transform controls, material, [snorts]'

[00:51] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: '[music] fresnel, environment, map, and more. We highly encourage you to explore these settings and see how they affect your shape. You can also use presets by selecting'

[01:04] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'them at the top of the inspector. And in the environment map settings, you\'ll find default images to start designing with. [music] In HANA, you start by creating a'

[01:19] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: '2D shape. With one click, you can turn it into a 3D object using this effect. Each 3D shape has its own 3D space, but it still behaves like a 2D element on'

[01:32] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'the canvas. [music] That means you can use the same layout, events, and interactions you already use in 2D, now applied to 3D. All 3D shape properties in Hana are'

[01:47] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'fully interactive. You can control things like depth, bevel, rotation, materials, [music] and all other properties using Hana\'s events and'

[01:59] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'actions all in real time. This makes it easy to animate between states, create pressed or hover effects, [music] follow event. It\'s a simple way to create dynamic 3D interactions'

[02:11] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'starting from the 2D shapes you already use. For the first time, HANA [music] supports true 3D shapes alongside 2D, all in one canvas. You can learn more'

[02:23] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'about this feature in our docs and our blog. Add [music] depth. Bring your designs to life with real-time interactivity and see what you can create. [music] In the next tutorial, we\'ll explore more about'

[02:35] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'this feature and create this design step by step together. Click on the bell so you don\'t miss it. See [music] you next time.'
